Package: tvrmst
Type: Package
Title: Time-Varying RMST from Survival Matrices
Version: 0.0.6
Authors@R: person(given = c("Imad"),
  family = "EL BADISY",
  role = c("aut", "cre"),
  email = "elbadisyimad@gmail.com")
Author: Imad EL BADISY [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Imad EL BADISY <elbadisyimad@gmail.com>
Description: Utilities for RMST and time-varying RMST quantities
  computed from survival curves provided on a time grid. Model-agnostic accepts
  only time vector and survival matrices, returning RMST-based quantities and
  bootstrap summaries.
